      "content": "Please know that what you are feeling is a very common and deeply painful creative block. It often feels permanent, but creative wells have cycles, and this intense dryness doesn't mean the well is gone. Try stepping completely away from your making for a while; instead, focus on absorbing something entirely different, whether it's nature, art you love, or just an uninterrupted walk. Small shifts in perspective can sometimes reveal the spark in a new form later on.",
